ge shipping fees and refurbishing compensation for any parts and packages that show signs of use or damage, as well as a $99 re-boxing fee.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-45_ pf-gs-heading-6 Title"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-47_">3. Return Process</span></h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-48_ pf-gs-heading-6 Title"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-50_">&nbsp;3.1 Shipping Cost</span></h3><p class="sc-jWUzzU cKWSZG pf-51_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-53_">We only provide free shipping for Damage/Defect/Fault on Arrival. Shipping of return for other reasons has to be paid by the customer. However, we can always help you get a much lower shipping price through our logistics network.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-54_ pf-gs-heading-6 Title"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-56_">3.2 Packing and Protection</span></h3><p class="sc-jWUzzU cKWSZG pf-57_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-59_">To prevent secondary damage, all items must be returned with original packaging and protection.  If you have lost the original packing, we can provide one at your cost.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-60_ pf-gs-heading-6 Title"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-62_">3.3 Risk on the Road</span></h3><p class="sc-jWUzzU cKWSZG pf-63_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj pf-65_">Any loss/damage during the return process due to improper packing or the actions/inactions of the logistics supplier shall be under your responsibility. We will carefully inspect the received parcel and our warehouse may reject the returned item if found severely damaged.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="s